@startuml

actor User
participant ":TransactionsList" as List
participant ":CurrencyConverter" as Converter
participant ":ExchangeRateData" as Rates

User -> List : request convert transaction(id, targetCurrency)
List -> List : getTransactionById(id)

List -> Converter : convert(amount, from, target)
activate Converter

Converter -> Rates : getRates()
Rates --> Converter : rates

Converter --> List : convertedAmount
deactivate Converter

List --> User : display converted value

note over Converter
Conversion is view-only.
Original transaction remains unchanged
unless user confirms.
end note

@enduml
